I"j<h1 id="how-books-are-made">How Books Are Made</h1>

<p><em>A podcast about the art and science of making books.</em></p>

<p>Host <a href="https://arthurattwell.com">Arthur Attwell</a> speaks to pioneers in design and production to find out how they made their books, and to answer your questions about making yours – whether you’re crafting books for print or screen, at a big company or a boutique publisher.</p>

